<item>
            <title>[LU-15447] sanity-flr/208 fail on new kernels</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15447</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;new kernel (e.g. 4.18.0-305.25.1) declares loopback devices in tmpfs as non-rotational, so Lustre re-export OSTs in tmpfs as non-rotational while sanity-flr/208 expect rotational by default.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
